MAIN CORE PACKAGES TO install

    - GnuPg
    - github
    - wget
    - curl


DROPBOX SETUP
    - git clone .dropbox folder
    - copy .dropbox folder to ~/$USER
    - copy dropybox.py to ~/$USER/BIN
    - chmod +x dropbox.py
    - start dropbox.py to get dropbox syncing
    - run ./dropbox.py commands see below. 
        - ./dropbox.py exclude add ~/Dropbox/MEDIA/
        - ./dropbox.py exclude add ~/Dropbox/PROJECTS/


    
